<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/ichada/3845339895/"><img loading="lazy" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2461/3845339895_5da533f0dc.jpg" alt="WordCamp China 2009/thruth&amp;rsquo;s Tee (by&lt;br&gt;
